description: Try our easy to follow Lamb Tagine recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Lamb Tagine Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 kg butterflied lamb shoulder Rosemary & mint

recipeInstructions.text: Add apricots and chickpeas. Change the cooker setting to HIGH and cook for 20 minutes. Serve lamb tagine with rice and garnish with parsley.
